targets.query:
from(bucket: "robots")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "encodeurs")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["robot"] == "${robot_name}")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["name"] == "two_wheels_encoders")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "gauche" or r["_field"] == "droit")
  |> aggregateWindow(every: v.windowPeriod, fn: mean, createEmpty: false)
  |> keep(columns: ["_time", "_field", "_value"])

from(bucket: "robots")

  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "distance" or r["_field"] == "orientation")
  |> aggregateWindow(every: v.windowPeriod, fn: mean, createEmpty: false)
  |> keep(columns: ["_time", "_field", "_value"])
